ActFamily Orders and Agreements Enforcement Assistance Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Family Support Orders and Agreements Garnishment Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the FAMILY SUPPORT ORDERS AND AGREEMENTS GARNISHMENT REGULATIONS, in order to enhance tools for enforcing support orders and agreements by adding two new sources of funds to the list of federal funds that may be garnisheed to satisfy family support debts and by allowing a provincial enforcement service to use electronic communications to submit garnishee summons.
